        <div class="comp-row"><span class="ci">✓</span><span data-lang="cs" class="on">CNC, 3D tisk, laser, prototyping — jeden partner</span><span data-lang="sk">CNC, 3D tlač, laser, prototyping — jeden partner</span><span data-lang="en">CNC, 3D print, laser, prototyping — one partner</span><span data-lang="de">CNC, 3D-Druck, Laser, Prototyping — ein Partner</span></div>
        <div class="comp-row"><span class="ci">✓</span><span data-lang="cs" class="on">Série od 1 kusu, bez minima</span><span data-lang="sk">Série od 1 kusu, bez minima</span><span data-lang="en">Series from 1 piece, no minimum</span><span data-lang="de">Serie ab 1 Stück, kein Minimum</span></div>
        <div class="comp-row"><span class="ci">✓</span><span data-lang="cs" class="on">Nabídka do 48 hodin</span><span data-lang="sk">Ponuka do 48 hodín</span><span data-lang="en">Quote in 48 hours</span><span data-lang="de">Angebot in 48 Stunden</span></div>
        <div class="comp-row"><span class="ci">✓</span><span data-lang="cs" class="on">Odpovídáme do 24 h, voláme osobně</span><span data-lang="sk">Odpovedáme do 24 h, voláme osobne</span><span data-lang="en">We respond in 24h, call personally</span><span data-lang="de">Wir antworten in 24h, rufen persönlich an</span></div>
        <div class="comp-row"><span class="ci">✓</span><span data-lang="cs" class="on">Jasná cena, bez skrytých poplatků</span><span data-lang="sk">Jasná cena, bez skrytých poplatkov</span><span data-lang="en">Clear price, no hidden fees</span><span data-lang="de">Klarer Preis, keine versteckten Gebühren</span></div>
